sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Provider (Stripe/Clever)
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant A as REST API
    participant Q as BullMQ Queue
    participant W as Webhook Worker
    participant D as PostgreSQL

    P->>G: POST /webhooks/{provider}
    G->>A: Forward request
    A->>A: Verify HMAC signature
    A->>A: Validate timestamp (< 5 min)
    A->>D: Check idempotency (provider, event_id)
    alt Duplicate event
        D-->>A: Already processed
        A-->>P: 200 OK
    else New event
        A->>D: INSERT webhook_events (unprocessed)
        A->>Q: Enqueue process_webhook job
        A-->>P: 200 OK
        Q->>W: Consume job
        W->>D: Load webhook_event
        W->>W: Process event (business logic)
        W->>D: SET processed_at
    end
